column6: Witness Zephyr Quinn's rampage across the face of the earth. Dare you dwell on the suicidal secrets of the Secret Cinema? Are you bold enough to gamble your life at Suki Boutique's casino? And when is Casanova Quinn in all this? Why has Sasa Lisi come now? What shocking secret do the victims on Zephyr's hit list lead to? The answer will blow the remaining unblown bits of your mind, Earthmen. By the attorneys of Fraction, Moon, Peter & Dharb.
